      <title>Rivian 需要证明，随着电动汽车需求放缓，它可以停止烧钱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/rivian-needs-to-show-it-can-stop-burning-cash-as-ev-demand-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rivian Automotive Inc. 早已失去了特斯拉公司最可信竞争对手的地位。现在，它应对电动汽车需求放缓的能力构成了最大的考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/rivian-needs-to-show-it-can-stop-burning-cash-as-ev-demand-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 12:46:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
